not gone to work not gone on a trip

10
00:00:35,066 --> 00:00:37,266
vanished into thin air

11
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:40,166
your baby is crying in the next room

12
00:00:40,266 --> 00:00:41,900
your servants are whispering

13
