six years pass

18
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:55,700
some sources say up to 15

19
00:00:57,033 --> 00:00:59,266
before this man shows up at your door

20
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:01,566
he's not your missing husband anymore

21
00:01:01,866 --> 00:01:03,400
he's become the Buddha

22
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,900
the enlightened one

23
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,233
the guy everyone's calling

24
00:01:08,233 --> 00:01:10,133
the greatest teacher who ever lived

25
00:01:11,433 --> 00:01:14,566
your still the wife he left behind

26
